Suntory, one of the global leaders in the beverage and food industry, has unveiled its new Lucozade variant, Lucozade Cola. Boma Harrison, the Head of Marketing & Trade Marketing at Suntory Beverage & Food Nigeria Limited (SBFN), at a media parley held in Lagos to launch the product, said the product is a result of evolving consumers’ needs, is intended to delight consumers and ensure refreshment needs are met. According to Harrison, Lucozade Cola, a glucose-based energy drink, with a cola flavour, is an extension of the Lucozade energy drink. The product will be available in the market by 1st (week in) December 2020. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! “Lucozade Cola gives pure, beneficial energy that stimulates mental and physical positivity of its consumers, which are largely the youths. With Lucozade Cola, now have the energy to get through it plus the fun side of Cola, ensuring the pursuit of your passion never stops. “Welcome to the Cooola side of Lucozade with Lucozade Cola. With all the negativity in the world, we all need some energy to go through it”. COVID-19: PenCom Postpones Retirees’ Verification, Enrolment Exercise Dangote Voted 2020 Best Company In CSR, Infrastructure Devt By PR Professionals Harrison also stated that, “Lucozade Cola is a vibrant drink intended for our vibrant consumers. They are the everyday, on-the-go men and women who consider themselves as hustlers and digital citizens. These are people leading full and busy lives and have an innate desire to progress and succeed. We want to provide our consumers with products that will enable them in the pursuit of their passions and also support their yearning for an ideal world that is free of negativity. “We want the brand to resonate with the lifestyle of our target audience which is fun, trendy and social. These are the value-conscious people wh